&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide CLASS reliability support to CLASS observers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct CLASS Observation Trainings for contracted observers serving the Observation Services Team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and support strong working relationships with observers and other team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support with CLASS written feedback audits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct in-person and video CLASS observations, including post-observation data entry&lt;/li&gt;
