&lt;li&gt;Document efficiencies for conducting observations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support various observation projects simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
